"title": "5967: thrift",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5967",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Saving by the careful use of resources. In general this is encouraged in Scripture, though the dangers of meanness, materialism and anxiety are recognised.</p>\n<h2>Encouragements to thrift</h2>\n<h3>To provide for the future</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:20\">PRO 21:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:6-Prov6:8\">PRO 6:6–6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:5\">PRO 10:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:27\">PRO 12:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:23-Prov27:27\">PRO 27:23–27:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:25\">PRO 30:25</a></p>\n<h3>To provide for children</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:14\">PSA 17:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:22\">PRO 13:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:14\">2CO 12:14</a></p>\n<h3>To provide for others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:28-Deut14:29\">DEU 14:28–14:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:2\">1CO 16:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:28\">EPH 4:28</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of thrift</h2>\n<h3>Noah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:21\">GEN 6:21</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Joseph</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:48\">GEN 41:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:28-Gen41:36\">GEN 41:28–41:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:53\">GEN 41:53</a></p>\n<h3>Solomon</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:17-1Kgs9:19\">1KI 9:17–9:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:4-2Chr8:6\">2CH 8:4–8:6</a></p>\n<h3>Jehoshaphat</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr17:12\">2CH 17:12</a></p>\n<h3>Hezekiah</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:27-2Chr32:29\">2CH 32:27–32:29</a></p>\n<h3>The good wife</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:13-Prov31:16\">PRO 31:13–31:16</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:12-John6:13\">JHN 6:12–6:13</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The dangers of thrift</h2>\n<h3>Meanness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:4-John12:6\">JHN 12:4–12:6</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:8-Matt26:9\">MAT 26:8–26:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:4-Mark14:5\">MRK 14:4–14:5</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:27-Prov3:28\">PRO 3:27–3:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:24\">PRO 11:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:26\">PRO 11:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:6-Prov23:8\">PRO 23:6–23:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:22\">PRO 28:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:13\">ECC 5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:6\">2CO 9:6</a></p>\n<h3>Materialism</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:15\">LUK 12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:8\">ECC 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:14\">MIC 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:16–12:21</a></p>\n<h3>Anxiety</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:22-Luke12:31\">LUK 12:22–12:31</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:25-Matt6:34\">MAT 6:25–6:34</a></p>\n<h2>Lack of thrift</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:13\">LUK 15:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:17\">PRO 21:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:20\">PRO 21:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:20-Prov23:21\">PRO 23:20–23:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:3\">PRO 29:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:1\">LUK 16:1</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual thrift</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:19-Matt6:21\">MAT 6:19–6:21</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:15-Eph5:16\">EPH 5:15–5:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:14\">PRO 10:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:19\">1TI 6:19</a></p>\n<h3>The wicked store up judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:5-Rom2:6\">ROM 2:5–2:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:7-Rom2:10\">ROM 2:7–2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:6-Rev18:7\">REV 18:6–18:7</a></p>",
